    {
      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user is showing a BSOD (Blue Screen of Death) with the stop code \"WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR\". They want me to:\n\n1. Investigate this using \"proper enterprise root cause analysis\"\n2. Give it a \"fixibility score using ifix\"\n3. Tell how reliable the fix is\n4. Whether they can improve PC temperature5. Check if components are okay without stress testing\n6. Use PowerShell/Python tools\n\nI'm currently in plan/read-only mode, so I can only read, search, and analyze. I cannot make any edits or run commands that modify the system.\n\nLet me start by:\n1. Understanding what WHEA_UNCORRECTABLE_ERROR means\n2. Checking the system for relevant logs and information\n3. Planning the investigation approach\n\nFirst, let me search for more information about this error and then examine the system.",
